{"type":"user","uuid":"d89c7276-632d-4f4c-9acf-50295e20efbf","session_id":"301af3e8-7399-4356-b525-ec1e2117384a","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019ce3c206eee0ee494393601bcdaa53","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Command: cd /Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw && npm test -- --test-name-pattern=\"F-012 SystemMonitorService\" 2>&1 | head -100\nStdout: \n> prizmclaw@0.1.0 test\n> node --test tests/**/*.test.js --test-name-pattern=F-012 SystemMonitorService\n\n▶ F-009 Config Variables\n  ▶ COMMAND_BLACKLIST\n    ✔ should default to empty array when not set (19.0315ms)\n    ✔ should parse comma-separated blacklist commands via parseCsvList (4.239291ms)\n  ✔ COMMAND_BLACKLIST (23.6145ms)\n  ▶ HIGH_RISK_KEYWORDS\n    ✔ should have default high-risk keywords (0.209375ms)\n  ✔ HIGH_RISK_KEYWORDS (0.322625ms)\n  ▶ DIRECT_EXEC_MODE\n    ✔ should default to false (0.20625ms)\n    ✔ should be a boolean (0.14825ms)\n  ✔ DIRECT_EXEC_MODE (0.477125ms)\n  ▶ Config object structure\n    ✔ should have all F-009 config properties (0.16ms)\n  ✔ Config object structure (0.289459ms)\n✔ F-009 Config Variables (25.203791ms)\n▶ F-011 AI CLI Config Variables\n  ▶ AI_CLI_HEARTBEAT_THRESHOLD_MS\n    ✔ should default to 10000ms (22.499834ms)\n    ✔ should be a non-negative integer (0.786292ms)\n  ✔ AI_CLI_HEARTBEAT_THRESHOLD_MS (23.572625ms)\n  ▶ AI_CLI_HEARTBEAT_INTERVAL_MS\n    ✔ should default to 30000ms (0.08975ms)\n    ✔ should be a non-negative integer (0.056583ms)\n  ✔ AI_CLI_HEARTBEAT_INTERVAL_MS (0.207333ms)\n  ▶ AI_CLI_ENABLE_HEARTBEAT\n    ✔ should default to true (0.074292ms)\n    ✔ should be a boolean (0.055667ms)\n  ✔ AI_CLI_ENABLE_HEARTBEAT (0.1895ms)\n  ▶ Config object structure\n    ✔ should have all F-011 config properties (0.072916ms)\n  ✔ Config object structure (0.1235ms)\n✔ F-011 AI CLI Config Variables (24.473417ms)\n✔ fixture-loader: getFixturePath returns correct path (0.691416ms)\n✔ fixture-loader: loadFixture loads file content (0.757167ms)